&lt;p&gt;Is it possible to tame a human mind without religion?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Is it necessary we need to tame a human mind or  &lt;br&gt;
all should have equal freedom to think and do?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Why use dos and don’ts of religion?  &lt;br&gt;
Why use heaven and hell of religion to bring humans to senses?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
